---
/** CTA final de la página de precios. */
---

<section
  class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-linear-to-br from-gray-50 to-indigo-50/80 dark:from-gray-950 dark:to-indigo-950/40 p-8 md:p-10 text-center space-y-4"
>
  <h2 class="m-0 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
    <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaTitle">¿Listo para ordenar tu stack?</span>
  </h2>
  <p class="m-0 mx-auto max-w-lg text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
    <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaSubtitle">Pide acceso y te respondemos en cuanto haya capacidad.</span>
  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center pt-2">
    <a
      href="/request-access"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-100 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white dark:text-gray-900 no-underline hover:opacity-95 transition-opacity"
    >
      <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaPrimary">Solicitar acceso</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="/"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 no-underline hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 transition-colors"
    >
      <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaSecondary">Volver al inicio</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
